58	/// pluml) the fixture name happens to equal a valid nameplate moniker — that's
59	/// the convention crucible-scoped tabtargets exploit when imprinting (e.g.,
60	/// `rbw-cC.Charge.{fixture}.sh`). Non-crucible fixtures (regime-*, calibrant-*,
61	/// canonical-*, etc.) carry their fixture name in this slot too, but no
62	/// nameplate-shaped consumer reads them.
