/// Pin upstream PlantUML by digest. Bind mode reads RBRV_BIND_IMAGE from
/// rbev-bottle-plantuml/rbrv.env and mirrors the digest into GAR — no
/// reliquary, no Dockerfile, no Cloud Build. Mirrors rbw-Odb step 2.
